channel.title: What do you think of 614's?
channel.description: As Im sure alot of you know I have a 614 server in development. I also released a tutorial on how to make a 614 webclient in the client hacking section. In my opinion they are fun and easy to code as well as very manageable and neat. I love what you can do with them, how stable they are, and surprisingly, how there are few glitches. What do you think of them?

item.title: What do you think of 614's?
item.dc:creator: @the_elve_age the elve age
item.description:
@the_elve_age wrote:

YES! I’m honestly tired of 317s. For the same reason you read about everyday. Its overused.
500+ are made so much better, the graphics are better, and there is a lot more to do.

317s were made in like 03. 7 years later people are still using a piece of crap. There is a reason Jagex advanced.

Anything above 370 is fine with me.

@614s. I personally like 562 graphics better, but 614 also have more weapons and monsters, so, it will be cool to see what the outcome of them are.
